/>\ne.g.: 721<br />\n仲未計呢家立法權 <br />\n原來仲可以玩埋緊急法<br />\n<br />\n無謂自命清高 仲話有險可守 <br />\n而係根本得法官律師 係無辦法守到<br />\n法治 唔係靠法官律師維繫<br />\n法治係一個系統<br />\n行政不公 立法不公 執法不公<br />\n連法官其實都只係由行政委任 對行政實在無任何抵抗力<br />\n<br />\n成個體制 根本就唔容許有法治<br />\n以往嘅&quot;公正公平&quot; 只係當權者唔插手干預<br />\n當佢要出手時 跟規矩 大家係無能為力"},{"pid":"c1356a14e7983e70b82ea45d4470a3c37d07ce4e","tid":1698112,"uid":56428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T10:26:44.000Z","msg":"港奸"},{"pid":"9a70d8e054c02a83d3cbfdbd8038eb1d6f595591","tid":1698112,"uid":230516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T10:27:56.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"9fd4ac7ce7c30b0db315f8fcf00fd2f0f1d664bf","tid":1698112,"uid":77180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T10:29:14.000Z","msg":"為乜呢"},{"pid":"ce67a052e989b85dca2230f7c1a9b34edb79f239","tid":1698112,"uid":171192,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"a4ade679cc9f711f5243ead082bf5b4cb673d3e3","tid":1698112,"uid":107405,"like":115,"dislike":2,"score":113,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T09:43:17.000Z","msg":"公文袋有時就係弊撚在呢樣野 <br />\n又唔諗下法治再咁比中共蠶食落去 <br />\n佢地呢班自覺高高在上既法律界人士 地位就變成同大陸維權律師一樣卑微<br />\n就機會比佢醫 先黎怕藥苦唔肯食就係呢挺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T10:30:26.000Z","msg":"班律師黨證明咗到咗關鍵時刻<br />\n私利大過天<br />\n如果講法治已死仲點搵銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以緊急法推咗，克警無法律管，手足被亂charge亂判<br />\n佢地都仲係嗰副嘴臉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92eaf969f5b8be2d904f9fb4ca96a8758a14a81e","tid":1698112,"uid":83251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T10:30:40.000Z","msg":"收皮啦，公民袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4441e51ee88e33ddd7e07f2